risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: "Resolved with a shared non-negative integer parser wired into create, update, and update-many planning."
expected_result: "Negative, fractional, and nonnumeric estimates fail before writes across all mutation paths."
actual_result: All invalid estimate forms return usage errors; zero and positive integers remain valid; focused and full tests passed.
